      "review_count": 16,
      "average_rating": 4.69,
      "html": "<div id=\"tab-reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--reviews panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\"><div id=\"reviews\" class=\"woocommerce-Reviews\"><div id=\"comments\"><h2 class=\"woocommerce-Reviews-title\">16 reviews for <span>Mobirite Buds</span></h2><ol class=\"commentlist\">\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1201\">\n<div id=\"comment-1201\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12a?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Arjun Sharma</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Transparent design looks very cool and futuristic. Everyone in my office asks about it. Sound quality is also very crisp with deep bass.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_6b27680997c244909e09918087ad5e0b.png\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1202\">\n<div id=\"comment-1202\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12b?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Suhail Khan</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Low latency mode is actually working. No sound lag while playing BGMI. Only issue is battery lasts 6 hours, not 8 as mentioned in heavy use.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_9b4121eb7293491cb8c108919a7f1a1b.png\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1203\">\n<div id=\"comment-1203\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12c?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Karthik R.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Initially my product had pairing issues and customer support agent didn't respond properly on call. But I mailed the head contact help.vyntech@gmail.com and issue was solved in 1 day. Excellent service later on. Pods are worth every rupee.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1204\">\n<div id=\"comment-1204\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12d?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 3 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:60%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">3</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Vikram Jha</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>ANC is okay but sound isolation could be better. Also touch controls are very sensitive, sometimes track changes while adjusting buds.</p></div>\n<div class=\"bt-review-reply-container\"><button class=\"bt-reply-toggle-btn\" onclick=\"btToggleReply(this)\">View reply by Vyntech <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i></button><div class=\"bt-reply-content\" style=\"display:none;\"><strong>Response from Vyntech</strong><p>Dear Vikram,<br><br>We apologize for the sensitivity issues. You can actually adjust the touch sensitivity via the firmware settings. Please mail us at help.vyntech@gmail.com and we will assign a product expert to guide you through the calibration process.<br><br>Best Regards,<br>Vyntech</p></div></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1205\">\n<div id=\"comment-1205\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12e?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Manoj Kumar</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Bohat hi mast product hai. Clear sound aur battery backup bhi solid hai. Packaging was very premium.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_9db71a3be25c442b89ad52a5d2b7fdb4.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1206\">\n<div id=\"comment-1206\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12f?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Saravanan</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Romba nalla irukku. Connection fast-ah connect aagudhu. Deep bass is just amazing for music lovers.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_708c97847524471482e787e1ba18041b.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1207\">\n<div id=\"comment-1207\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12g?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Nitin P.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Good product but delivery was delayed by 3 days. Thankfully Vyntech support was helpful. Product works perfectly.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1208\">\n<div id=\"comment-1208\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12h?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Sneha Reddy</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Chala bagundi product. Transparent case looks very premium and sound quality is 10/10.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_db6a7158747844dc9d334486122e6f45.jpeg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1209\">\n<div id=\"comment-1209\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12i?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Rahul S.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Best earbuds in this budget. The ENC works really well for office calls, background noise is almost zero.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/better95159-hub/betteresttech-uploads@main/reviews/blobio-imr_e38a60f975f644ca9e0b2cdfe44d7bed.jpg\" alt=\"Review Image\" class=\"bt-review-img\" onclick=\"btOpenLightbox(this.src)\" style=\"width:70px; height:70px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; margin-top:10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n</div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1210\">\n<div id=\"comment-1210\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12j?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Preeti V.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Using it for my gym workouts. IPX5 handles sweat perfectly. Fit is very stable, doesn't fall out.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1211\">\n<div id=\"comment-1211\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12k?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 4 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:80%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">4</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Manish G.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Sound is great but case is slightly small, feels like it might slip from hand. But build quality of buds is excellent.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1212\">\n<div id=\"comment-1212\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12l?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Anjali T.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Super quality sound and very easy to pair with both Google assistant and Siri.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1213\">\n<div id=\"comment-1213\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12m?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Deepak Rao</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Best value for money product on Vyntech. Transparent design is a head turner.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1214\">\n<div id=\"comment-1214\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12n?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Swati S.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Received product in good condition. Bass is heavy as I like it. Battery backup is around 7 hours.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1215\">\n<div id=\"comment-1215\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12o?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Manoj Das</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Here is my own review for this product: what I found. Fast pairing, great sound. Had a minor delivery delay but product is excellent.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n<li class=\"review\" id=\"li-comment-1216\">\n<div id=\"comment-1216\" class=\"comment_container\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/12p?s=60&d=mm&r=g\" class=\"avatar avatar-60\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\">\n<div class=\"comment-text\">\n<div class=\"star-rating\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><span style=\"width:100%\">Rated <strong class=\"rating\">5</strong> out of 5</span></div>\n<p class=\"meta\"><strong class=\"woocommerce-review__author\">Amit G.</strong> <em class=\"woocommerce-review__verified verified\" style=\"font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: 800; color: #16a34a; margin-left: 4px;\">(verified purchase)</em> &ndash; <time class=\"woocommerce-review__published-date\">April 26, 2026</time></p>\n<div class=\"description\"><p>Worth the money. Go for it if you want premium looking earbuds with solid performance.</p></div>\n</div></div></li>\n\n</ol></div><div class=\"clear\"></div></div></div>"
